    <item>
      <title>马科斯推动菲律宾团结，杜特尔特猛烈抨击继任者</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-28/marcos-calls-for-unity-as-duterte-s-son-seeks-his-resignation</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周日，菲律宾总统小费迪南德·马科斯和他的前任罗德里戈·杜特尔特分别举行集会，吸引了数千名支持者，凸显出日益加深的分歧，可能会导致赢得 2022 年大选的该国最有权势的政治家族联盟的分裂。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-28/marcos-calls-for-unity-as-duterte-s-son-seeks-his-resignation</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 28 Jan 2024 16:35:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国收紧证券借贷规则以支持股市</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-28/china-suspends-lending-of-some-securities-for-short-selling</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国证券监管机构周日宣布，中国将从周一开始停止某些股票的卖空借贷，以支撑中国股市的暴跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-28/china-suspends-lending-of-some-securities-for-short-selling</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 28 Jan 2024 07:40:46 GMT</pubDate>
